    "UIName": "Taipan",
    "Id": "chassisdef_taipan_TPN-89",
    "Name": "Taipan",
    "Details": "The TPN-89 is the base Taipan configuration, built around a MASC system in the right torso that enables burst speeds exceeding 150 kilometers per hour on a quadrupedal 25-ton frame. Two torso-mounted Light PPCs provide accurate fire at extended ranges with no heat concerns under normal operation. A center-torso Streak SRM 2 fed by a ton of left-torso ammunition offers reliable close-range backup that only fires on confirmed lock. Light Ferro-Fibrous armor keeps the frame protected within its weight class.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Jammer</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_taipan_3160"
  },
  "VariantName": "TPN-89",
  "ChassisTags": {
    "items": [
      "ArmLimitUpperLeft",
